Hi <%= @user.name || 'there' %>,

We received a request to reset the password for your Untethered account associated with this email address.

To choose a new password, please click the link below or paste it into your browser:

<%= edit_password_reset_url(@reset_token, email: @user.email, subdomain: @operator.subdomain) %>

This link will expire in two hours for your security.

If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email and your password will remain unchanged.

If you have any questions or need further assistance, please contact our support team.

Thank you
